reviewText: This was a weird movie- it wasn't really funny. However it did hold my attention right to the end. The plot is so twisted and the characters so colorful, that you can't help but finish it. I don't know, I sort of liked it- which in itself is weird.
It was engaging and kept your attention as another reviewer said but I could not get with the sense of humor in this film, found it a little disturbing
A very strange movie indeed.  Weirdest thing I have ever watched but for some reason it held my attention.  Strangest yet most interesting movie I have ever seen...
This movie is truly a blend of urbanistic selfishness and cultural burden to emmancipation.  One has to balance himself on top to escape these two opposite but selfish environments.
